CGI-Safe version 1.24
=====================

Makes running the CGI environment safer by eliminating dangerous %ENV
variables and presetting certain CGI.pm globals.  See POD for complete 
details and use.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

 CGI.pm 2.20 or newer

